{"id": "1474253580918587463", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1149612289020936212", "author_name": "hana0406", "author_bot": false, "content": "質問です\n無料でもらえるSSRを24にして、久遠ガチャはサルバドルの凸と札を狙うのがいいかなと思っているのですが、他におすすめあれば教えていただきたいです！\n手持ちキャラは以下で、限定札はダフォのみ所持です\nちなみに目下の目標は融災350です(前回は340でした)", "timestamp": "2026-02-20T03:57:23.998000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1474253579282939994", "filename": "Screenshot_20260219-224743.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2107028, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1474253579282939994/Screenshot_20260219-224743.png?ex=6a336ca3&is=6a321b23&hm=ec3297927848dfd5d805439df3f93d6edec313621444d0038972cdc6f921061a&"}, {"id": "1474253580100964523", "filename": "Screenshot_20260219-224750.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2117834, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1474253580100964523/Screenshot_20260219-224750.png?ex=6a336ca3&is=6a321b23&hm=6fc8f2e6641561b7c3a239ab4d788e7b23cc71b83a099edc2f6f65f37ae1d815&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1474254213981671576", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1149612289020936212", "author_name": "hana0406", "author_bot": false, "content": "高難度とかはダフォカーシアファイント+救援サルバドルでいってます", "timestamp": "2026-02-20T03:59:54.932000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
